&lt;p data-start=&quot;486&quot; data-end=&quot;763&quot;&gt;As a Software Developer at CapIntel, you’ll contribute to building backend solutions that support client onboarding and integrations. You’ll work hands-on implementing backend services, supporting client requirements, and helping ensure our platform scales alongside growing client demand.&amp;nbsp;In this role, you’ll collaborate closely with internal partners across Implementation, Data, and Product, and occasionally work with client technical teams to support integrations and resolve technical challenges. You’ll contribute to delivering reliable, high-quality solutions while continuing to grow your technical skills in a collaborative environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1124&quot; data-end=&quot;1287&quot;&gt;This role is ideal for someone who enjoys solving practical engineering problems, working across teams, and building software that directly impacts client success.&lt;/p&gt;
